	<h2> CSS TAGS!!!!!</h2>
	<h4> COLOR</h4>
		
		<p> <b>color</b>= selects the color of the text</p>
	
	<h4> BACKGROUND</h4>

		<p> <b>background-attachment</b>= Sets whether of not a background picture is fixed or scrolls with the webpage</p>
		<p> <b>background-color</b>= specifies the color of the background</p>
		<p> <b>background-image</b>= specifies the image that'll be in the background</p>
		<p> <b>background-position</b>= specifies the placement of the background image</p>
		<p> <b>background-siz</b>e= specifies the size of the background image</p>
	
	<h4> BASIC BOX</h3>
		
			<p> <b>height</b>= sets the height</p>
			<p> <b>margin</b>= sets all margin properties(for specifics you can use margin-left, margin-right, margin-top, margin-bottom)</p>
			<p> <b>padding</b>= sets all of the padding properties(for specifics you can use padding-left, padding-right, padding-top, padding-bottom)</p>
			<p> <b>width</b>= sets the width</p>
			<p> <b>postion</b>= specifies the type of postitioning method used for an element (static, relative, absolute, fixed)</p>
			<p> <b>.my-button</b>= creates a button</p>

	<h4> FONT</h4>
	
			<p> <b>font-family</b>= specifies the family of the text</p>
			<p> <b>font-size</b>= specifies the size of the font</p>
			<p> <b>font-weigh</b>x= specifies the weight of the font</p>

			
		


